This file needs to be populated with CA cert data 
for the Thales CTM Instance

Ensure that user has Login Certificate configured on their account. 

Information Available here:
https://thalesdocs.com/ctp/cm/2.8/admin/cm_admin/certificate-based-auth/index.html

1. Login to Thales CTM with an Admin account
2. On the left hand side, under "CA" - click on "Local"
3. Add local CA if none exists, 
    or download the existing CA (use ... on right hand side next to cert)
